window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>You can listen to this family-friendly story for free on your device with the Audible Stories Skill. Just say “Alexa, read me a nighttime story,” or “Alexa, read me a story” to hear more free genres.</b></p> <p>'What are we to do about the bees?' asks the ant to the butterfly, in this gentle eco tale.</p> <p>For the first time in ant’s memory, butterfly has no words of comfort. A newly hatched butterfly thinks he has an answer, but it will require many wings and great cooperation.</p> <p>An uplifting story that brings new meaning to the phrase 'the butterfly effect'.</p>"; 
